---
// src/components/sections/WhyChooseSection.astro
---
<section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-white border-t border-brand-border/40">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
            <div>
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-brand-navy mb-8">Why Teams Choose TheEduAssist</h2>
                <div class="bg-brand-softBg p-8 rounded-2xl border border-brand-border">
                    <p class="text-lg text-brand-textMain font-medium italic mb-6">
                        "We don't just build the website. We build the learning experience."
                    </p>
                    <a href="/about/" class="inline-flex items-center text-brand-accent font-bold hover:text-brand-primary transition-colors focus-ring">
                        More about our approach
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"></path></svg>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div>
                <ul class="space-y-6">
                    {[
                        "We understand both learning design and platform setup.",
                        "We structure content so learners know exactly what to do next.",
                        "We build systems that support selling, teaching, onboarding, and delivery.",
                        "We support Kajabi, LMS platforms, content files, templates, and launch workflows.",
                        "We help creators, coaches, consultants, educators, and training businesses move from scattered content to structured online learning."
                    ].map(point => (
                        <li class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                            <div class="mt-1 bg-brand-softGreen text-brand-accent rounded-full p-1 shrink-0">
                                <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                            </div>
                            <span class="text-lg text-brand-textMain leading-relaxed">{point}</span>
                        </li>
                    ))}
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
